        public PartList.Builder resolving()
        Allows part values to contain SVL variables.

        Resolves variables in part values when using the following methods:

        • append(String,Object)
        • append(String,Supplier<?>)
        • prepend(String,Object)
        • prepend(String,Supplier<?>)
        • set(String,Object)
        • set(String,Supplier<?>)
        • set(String,Object)
        • set(String,Supplier<?>)

        Uses VarResolver.DEFAULT to resolve variables.

        This object.
